tm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:12.960" end="00:13.203">In</span> <span begin="00:13.203" end="00:13.582">command</span> <span begin="00:13.582" end="00:13.812">where</span> <span begin="00:13.812" end="00:13.939">you</span> <span begin="00:13.939" end="00:14.507">belong</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">执掌指挥权，实至名归</span></p><p begin="00:14.307" end="00:15.670" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:14.307" end="00:14.520">How</span> <span begin="00:14.520" end="00:14.693">you</span> <span begin="00:14.693" end="00:14.960">say,</span> <span begin="00:14.960" end="00:15.195">no</span> <span begin="00:15.195" end="00:15.670">sweat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就像你说的，小菜一碟</span></p><p begin="00:15.712" end="00:18.040" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:15.712" end="00:15.912">We're</span> <span begin="00:15.912" end="00:16.163">finally</span> <span begin="00:16.163" end="00:16.304">on</span> <span begin="00:16.304" end="00:16.504">the</span> <span begin="00:16.504" end="00:16.803">field,</span> <span begin="00:16.803" end="00:16.968">we've</span> <span begin="00:16.968" end="00:17.219">had</span> <span begin="00:17.219" end="00:17.552">quite</span> <span begin="00:17.552" end="00:17.720">a</span> <span begin="00:17.720" end="00:18.040">run</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们终于踏上了战场，经历了一段不平凡的征程</span></p><p begin="00:18.291" end="00:20.592" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:18.291" end="00:19.150">Immigrants,</span> <span begin="00:19.150" end="00:19.355">we</span> <span begin="00:19.355" end="00:19.641">get</span> <span begin="00:19.641" end="00:19.809">the</span> <span begin="00:19.809" end="00:20.102">job</span> <span begin="00:20.102" end="00:20.592">done</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">移民，我们总能把活儿干漂亮</span></p><p begin="00:21.645" end="00:22.912" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:21.645" end="00:21.919">So</span> <span be